author: Brent Larkin, cleveland.com
title: Cleveland Mayor Frank Jackson is favorite to win a 4th term - for now: Brent Larkin
text: Cleveland Mayor Frank Jackson is a good man who has been a fiscally responsible steward. But after three terms in office, a focused, organized, well-funded campaign against him might make a strong case for a new direction, writes Brent Larkin.
